WorkItem.Description:
Error types which have been explicitly entered in cells are not read by PHPExcel_Reader_Excel5. Instead they are ignored.
 
#DIV/0!, #N/A, #NAME?, #NULL!, #NUM!, #REF!, #VALUE!
 
Behavior of PHPExcel_Reader_Excel5 should correspond to behavior of PHPExcel_Reader_Excel2007. Here error types are read as strings
 
'#DIV/0!', '#N/A', '#NAME?', '#NULL!', '#NUM!', '#REF!', '#VALUE!'
WorkItem.Summary: PHPExcel_Reader_Excel5 not reading explicitly entered error types in cells
